title: Lout of Count's Family
description: Kim Roksu lived a miserable, unimportant life until he transmigrated into Birth of a Hero, a fantasy novel. Unfortunately, he adopted the body of Cale Henituse, a minor villain who receives the beating of a lifetime from the main character, Choi Han. With this second chance, Kim is intent on living a happy, uneventful life. And the first step to that life is avoiding Choi Han at all costs!
